  - Releases now generate .bz2 files and display contents and checksums
- Translation Updates:
  Albanian, Catalan, Chinese (China), Chinese (Taiwan), Czech, Danish, Dutch,
  French, Galician, German, Italian, Japanese, Norwegian Bokmål, Russian,
